{"id":1217,"date":"2025-04-11T01:01:09","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T18:01:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1217"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:01","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:01","slug":"mesotherapy-nam","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/mesotherapy-nam\/","title":{"rendered":"Mesotherapy n\u00e1m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: da n\u00e1m, da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n, t\u00e0n nhang&#8230;<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ee8c ch\u1ebf s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin, k\u00edch th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, trung ho\u00e0 g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u cho da t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/li>\n<li>Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>V\u1edbi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mesotherapy s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea7u kim ti\u00eam vi \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u01b0a ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o trung b\u00ec c\u1ee7a da. C\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e3y li\u00ean k\u1ebft n\u00e1m v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c n\u00e1m v\u1edbi Tranexamic Acid 3%, 4-n-Butylresorcinol 1%, Alpha Arbutin 0.5%, Niacinamide 5% ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba, l\u00e0m m\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0u da, duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3 in 1: Duy tr\u00ec &#8211; Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i &#8211; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 45 ph\u00fat.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 14 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -6px; top: 44.0312px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: da n\u00e1m, da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n, t\u00e0n nhang&#8230;<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3576,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[57],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1217","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-meso-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1217","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1217"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3576"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1217"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1217"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\